  18 May 2004; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.8.5.ebuild,
  ntfsprogs-1.9.0.ebuild, ntfsprogs-1.9.1.ebuild:
  QA fix - added gnome to IUSE as per bug #51327. Thanks to Matt Taylor
  <liverbugg@juno.com>

*ntfsprogs-1.9.1 (01 May 2004)

  01 May 2004; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.9.1.ebuild:
  Version bumped. Closes 49560

  27 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.7.1.ebuild:
  Add inherit eutils

  25 Apr 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.9.0.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc, required by some packages which are useful on ppc.

*ntfsprogs-1.9.0 (02 Apr 2004)

  02 Apr 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> +ntfsprogs-1.9.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. Closes bug #44354. 1.8.5 is now marked stable on
  X86.

*ntfsprogs-1.8.5 (06 Mar 2004)

  06 Mar 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.8.0.ebuild,
  ntfsprogs-1.8.5.ebuild: Version bump; bug #43421. Old version
  removed as it had leaks in the directory lookup and handling code.

  01 Feb 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.8.0.ebuild,
  files/ntfsprogs-1.8.0-2.6-headers.patch:
  Added a patch to get ntfsprogs to compile on 2.6 headers; closes bug #39106.

